{
  "id": "adv_main_04_03_01",
  "title": "星空編1章11話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――トリエルがサニピに敗北した、翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The day after TRINITYAiLE's defeat by Sunny Peace",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyo-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 2.0000000079
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（昨日のライブバトルで、サニーピースは）\n（TRINITYAiLEを圧倒する強さを見せた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（In yesterday's live battle‚ Sunny Peace）\n（showed overwhelming power over TRINITYAiLE）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（だが勝者のさくらは以前のように笑えていなかった）\n（あの時感じた違和感……やはり気になるな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（But the winner‚ Sakura wasn't smiling like before）\n（That strange feeling I felt then… I'm still worried）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.9898378589,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……少し時間、いい……？\n聞きたいことがある……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san… can I have a‚ moment…?\nI have something to ask…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.5333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 55.079356899998544,
          "startTime": 17.2
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "構わないが、どうしたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't mind‚ but what's wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.4008842865,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依さんの様子、知りたい……その……\n昨日の敗戦で……落ち込んでないか、気になって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to know about Rui-san's condition… well…\nI'm worried that… she might be feeling down‚ from yesterday's defeat…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "大差で負けたからな。ショックだったはずだが……\nライブ直後は特に変わった様子はなかったぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She lost by a huge margin. It must be a shock…\nShe didn't seem particularly different right after the live battle",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "心配なら直接本人と話してみたらどうだ？\nトリエルの三人は今日一日オフだから、寮にいるはずだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you're worried‚ why don't you talk to her directly?\nTRINITYAiLE members have the day off today‚ so they should be at the dorms",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "直接話す……？\n「私達に負けて今どんな気持ち？」って聞くの……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Talk directly…?\nAre you asking me to ask her 'How do you feel now‚ after losing to us?'…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 58.3497730493
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "う……それは確かに聞き辛いな……すまない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… That's certainly hard to ask… I'm sorry…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.3497730493,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "それに、あの瑠依さんが大人しく休むとも思えない……\n昨日の敗戦の後なら、なおさら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ I don't think Rui-san will be able to rest quietly…\nEspecially‚ after yesterday's defeat…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（追い詰められると、人は思いがけない行動を）\n（することがある。琴乃が月ストを脱退したように……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（When people are pushed to the limit‚ they can do）\n（unexpected things. Like Kotono left from Moon Tempest…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな、俺の方でも瑠依達を気に掛けておくよ\n何事もなければいいが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're right‚ I'll keep an eye on TRINITYAiLE members\nI hope nothing happens…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-02-000-noon",
      "startTime": 87.4967562913
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 87.7467562913
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "（まだまだ、この程度のレベルじゃ）\n（昨日のサニピには到底敵わない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Still‚ only at this level）\n（Can't possibly match the Sunny Peace of yesterday）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.7809738714
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "（サニピに勝つには、もっと洗練させないと）\n（もっと速く、もっと大きく、もっと、もっと……！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（To beat Sunny Peace‚ I have to be more refined）\n（More faster‚ more bigger‚ more‚ more…!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.8494937498,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-02-000-noon",
      "startTime": 106.9934460163
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……ダメだわ……いくら練習しても\n昨日のサニピを超えるイメージが出来ない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa‚ haa… I can't… No matter how much I practice\nI can't imagine that surpasses Sunny Peace yesterday…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "サニピのあの強さは\nBIG4という立場が生み出したもの……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sunny Peace's that power was\na product of their position as one of BIG4…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "強さを期待され、日本中から注目されて、負けられない\n重圧の中で勝ち続けてきたから得られた強さ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Expected to be strong‚ watched by the whole of Japan‚ and the power\ngained from constantly winning under unbearable pressure…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "差が開くのも当然だわ、私達とは環境が違い過ぎる\nそんな相手に、どうしたら追いつけるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's natural that there're differences‚ the environment is so different from ours\nHow can we catch up‚ with such an opponent?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.6333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8581.589166399994,
          "startTime": 139.5
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "……あら？　自主練していたのね\nライブ明けなのによくやるわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Oh? You've been practicing on your own\nYou're doing well even though it's the day after the live battle",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.9,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 139.54840499999932,
          "startTime": 140.5333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 146.4187965314
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "mihoさん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "miho-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.4187965314,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "私のことは気にしなくていいわよ\n忘れ物を取りに来ただけだから、すぐ帰るわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't care about me\nI just came to get something I forgot‚ so I'll be back soon",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "……それにしても、昨日の敗戦が随分と堪えたようね\n今の貴方の目、とても見覚えがあるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…But‚ yesterday's defeat really hit you hard\nYour eyes now‚ look so familiar",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "スリクスに負けて心が折れたアイドル達と同じ……\n絶望して諦めた負け犬の目よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just like the idols who were heartbroken after losing to ⅢX…\nThe eyes of a loser who's given up in despair",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "わ、私は絶望なんてしていません！\n努力を続けていれば、いつかサニピに追いついて――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I'm not in despair!\nIf I keep trying‚ I'll catch up with Sunny Peace someday――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "本気で思っているの？　本当は分かっているはずよ\nこのままでは永遠にサニピには追いつけないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do you really think so? You probably know the truth\nAt this rate‚ you'll never catch up with Sunny Peace",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_01-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことない……私は……私達は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's not true… I'm… we're…",
        "id": ""
